additionalProperty.value:
INGREDIENTS LIST:

Vegetable Basmati Rice (57%), Chicken Biryani Sauce (43%).

Vegetable Basmati Rice contains: Water, Basmati Rice, Carrot (13%), Green Beans (9%), Canola Oil, Biryani Spice Mix [Spices (Turmeric, Paprika, Cardamom, Fenugreek, Cumin, Cinnamon, Chilli, Ginger, Fennel, Pepper, Clove, Coriander), Salt, Rice Flour, Dehydrated Garlic, Dehydrated Tomato, Yeast Extract, Bayleaf, Natural Colours (Turmeric, Paprika Oleoresins)], Mint, Coriander, Salt.

Chicken Biryani Sauce contains: Cooked RSPCA Approved Australian Chicken Breast (22%), Chopped Masala (19%) [Onion, Tomato, Sunflower Oil, Garlic, Ginger, Tomato Paste, Spices, Salt, Cumin Seeds, Chilli Powder, Preservative (224)], Tomato [Tomato, Acidity Regulator (330), Mineral Salt (509)], Yoghurt (Milk), Water, Biryani Spice ;Mix (1.5%) [contains Natural Colours (Turmeric, Paprika Oleoresins)], Canola Oil, Cumin, Ground Coriander Seed, Crushed Ginger, Crushed Garlic, Mint, Chilli Powder, Coriander, Corn Starch, Turmeric, Chicken Stock Seasoning, Salt

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Food Warnings: Despite careful inspection some bones may remain.

description: A warmly spiced curry with Australian chicken breast, biryani sauce and vegetable basmati rice.
name: Kitchen Chicken Biryani
